com.symyx.draw
Class ImageGenerator

java.lang.Object
  com.symyx.draw.ImageGenerator

public class ImageGenerator
extends java.lang.Object

Class that paints an image of a molecule or reaction to the image object you have written. For example, 

    ImageGenerator MyImageGenerator = new ImageGenerator();
    URL url = new URL(“http://www.myServer.com/molfiles/myMol.mol”);
    MyImageGenerator.setMolecule(url);

    BufferedImage myImage = new BufferedImage (200,200, BufferedImage.TYPE_INT_RGB);
    MyImageGenerator.paint(myImage);
    FileOutputStream fos = new FileOutputStream(“image.png”);
    ImageIO.write(myImage, “png”, fos);
    fos.close();
